OL,3,CHumber Bridge toll changes: What are
OL,4,Cthe new rules?
OL,6,FA new toll system is being introduced
OL,7,Fon the Humber Bridge that will see
OL,8,Ffees rise for the first time in 13
OL,9,Fyears.
OL,11,FMotorists will no longer be able to
OL,12,Fpay at manned toll booths and will
OL,13,Fneed to pay either in advance or by
OL,14,Fmidnight on the day after the crossing
OL,15,For risk having to pay a fee of #25.
OL,17,FThe new system will capture vehicle
OL,18,Finformation each time it crosses, in
OL,19,Fboth directions.
OL,21,FHere's everything you need to know.
