OL,3,CHumber Bridge toll changes: What are
OL,4,Cthe new rules?
OL,6,FThe new rules will officially start on
OL,7,FMonday 2 February, so those travelling
OL,8,Fover the weekend, 31 January or 1
OL,9,FFebruary, will have until 3 February
OL,10,Fto pay.
OL,12,FPayments can be made on the Humber
OL,13,FBridge website and there will also be
OL,14,Foptions to pay by phone, or to pre-pay
OL,15,Fby cash or card at shops which offer
OL,16,Fthe Paypoint scheme.
OL,18,FDrivers can register for a pre-pay
OL,19,Faccount on the Humber Bridge website,
OL,20,Fwhere money can be added to an account
OL,21,Fin advance for automatic payment.
