OL,3,CHumber Bridge toll changes: What are
OL,4,Cthe new rules?
OL,6,FPrices for cars to cross the bridge
OL,7,Fwill rise from #1.50 to #2 each way,
OL,8,Fbut account holders will pay 25% less.
OL,10,FIf payment isn't made online by
OL,11,Fmidnight the day after their crossing
OL,12,Fmotorists will be charged a #25 fee.
OL,14,FWhat are the charges?
OL,16,FDrivers are advised to check the
OL,17,FHumber Bridge website for concessions,
OL,18,Fpeople eligible to be exempt from the
OL,19,Ftoll charges and how to apply for a
OL,20,Fconcessions account.
