OL,3,CHumber Bridge toll changes: What are
OL,4,Cthe new rules?
OL,6,FAndrew Arundel, chief executive at the
OL,7,FHumber Bridge, said it was important
OL,8,FHumber Bridge users understand what
OL,9,Fthey need to do before, during, and
OL,10,Fafter the go-live weekend.
OL,12,FHe said: "Humber Bridge toll is a much-
OL,13,Fimproved payment system for Humber
OL,14,FBridge users, whether they choose to
OL,15,Fpay automatically via an account, or
OL,16,Fmanually for each crossing they make."
