OL,3,CHumber Bridge toll changes: What are
OL,4,Cthe new rules?
OL,6,F"It significantly builds on the
OL,7,Fexisting payment options, such as by
OL,8,Fintroducing a much more user-friendly
OL,9,Fpayment website, and increases the
OL,10,Fmethods of payment open to users with
OL,11,Fthe launch of a dedicated payment app
OL,12,Fand the ability to pay at PayPoint
OL,13,Flocations.
OL,15,F"Users will still be able to pay over
OL,16,Fthe phone, too, by speaking to one of
OL,17,Four customer services colleagues."
